condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Annual work plan | Description :The Project Implementation Entity shall prepare an annual work plan for theimplementation of the Project during the following yearby no later than November 30 of each year. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Audited Financial Statements | Description :The Borrower shall furnish to the Bank the audited FinancialStatements not later than six months after the end of each fiscal yearof the Borrower. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Interim unaudited financial reports | Description :The Borrower shall furnish to the Bank interim unauditedfinancial reports not later than 60 days after the end of each calendar semester. | Frequency :SemiAnnual
Finance Agreement :Mid-term review report | Description :The Project Implementation Entity shall furnish to the Bank a consolidatedmid-term review report. | Due Date :30-Jun-2017
Finance Agreement :Project Reports | Description :The Borrower shall furnish to the Bank Project Reports not later than 60 daysafter the end of each calendar semester. | Frequency :SemiAnnual

Finance Agreement :Public transport policy study | Description :Mengzi Municipality and Jianshui County shall have undertaken astudy, under terms of reference acceptable to the Bank, to review the regulation, financing, concession and subsidizationarrangements of its respective public transport sector. | Due Date :31-Dec-2016
